      }
    },
    "rich_text_Giy4ya": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_NcMXLa": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "How to Use for Best Results",
            "heading_tag": "h3"
          }
        },
        "richtext_cTpQ9L": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Discover how to get the most out of your Mumu Bath body wash. Follow these simple steps for a refreshing, nourishing, and eco friendly experience.</p><ol><li><strong>Wet Your Skin Thoroughly</strong> – Begin with warm water to open pores and prep your skin for a deeper cleanse.</li><li><strong>Lather Up Gently</strong> – Rub the eco friendly body wash bar between your hands or on a sponge to create a soft, creamy lather.</li><li><strong>Massage in Circular Motions</strong> – Apply the lather in gentle, circular motions to help boost circulation and enhance absorption.</li><li><strong>Let the Ingredients Work</strong> – Leave the lather on your skin for 30–60 seconds to allow natural oils and botanicals to deeply nourish.</li><li><strong>Rinse with Cool Water</strong> – Rinse off completely with cool or lukewarm water to close pores and seal in moisture.</li><li><strong>Pat Dry & Moisturize</strong> – Gently pat your skin dry with a towel and follow up with a natural moisturizer to lock in hydration for healthy body wash results.</li><li><strong>Store Properly Between Uses</strong> – Keep your bar in a dry, ventilated spot to extend its life and maintain hygiene.</li></ol>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "heading_NcMXLa",
        "richtext_cTpQ9L"
      ],
