    "rich_text_WmCxtA": {
      "type": "rich-text",
      "blocks": {
        "heading_7wBraP": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "Wrap Up Your Routine with Clean, Conscious Care",
            "heading_tag": "h3"
          }
        },
        "richtext_8UymQB": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Our body wash bars offer a refreshing cleanse without compromise - gentle on skin, tough on buildup, and kind to the planet. Made with natural, nourishing ingredients, each bar turns your daily shower into a self-care ritual. From sensitive skin to eco-conscious routines, there’s a bar for everyone. Explore the collection and elevate your everyday clean.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
